message:
Postal worker meets victim he helped get to safety.
"A postal worker from Sacramento, California, is being credited with rescuing a 16-year-old girl who had become a victim of sex trafficking."

data.description: A postal worker from Sacramento, California, is being credited with the rescue of a 16-year-old girl who became a victim of sex trafficking.
data.title: California Postal Worker Rescues 16-Year-Old Girl From Sex Traffickers
